el> </div> </div> </div> <input name="trialFromPage" id="trialFromPage" type="hidden" value="AutoTrial"/> {{/if}} {{/if}} </div>  </div> <div class="ml40 mr40 mt40"> <div class="zps-primary-button" id="startProjectTour">Get Started</div> </div>  </div>  </div>  </div>  </div> <div class="bgcontainer">   <div class="cloud1"></div>  <div class="cloud2"></div>  <div class="cloud3"></div>  <div class="bottomphase1"></div>  <div class="tree1"></div>  <div class="tree2"></div>  </div> {{if !Utils.isBugPortal}} <div style="" class="posrel img_div2 fl" id="welcomeScreenImgContainer"> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeTaskImg" style="" onviewport="true"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart" style="opacity: 1;">Tasks</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_01_Tasks_Subtasks.svg" class="gstImg1" style="transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart" style="opacity: 1;">Custom fields and custom views help you personalize tasks to suit specific business requirements.</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeTimesheetImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart">Timesheet</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_04_Timesheet.svg" class="gstImg4" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">Using the Timesheet you can easily record the clock-in and clock-out details logged by the users for tasks and issues.</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeDependencyImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart">Dependency</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_05_Gantt_Dependency.svg" class="gstImg5" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">Manage your task workflow better with task dependencies! Visualize the task sequence and link them effortlessly using the Gantt charts.</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeIssueImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart" style="">Issues</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_03_Tasks_Issues.svg" class="gstImg2" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">Follow up issues and fix them with appropriate resolutions. Stay on top of issues using Business Rules and SLAs.</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeMilestoneImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart">Milestones</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_02_Milestones.svg" class="gstImg3" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">Get your project started by creating Milestones, accomplish your major to-do lists and stay ahead of your project!</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeResourceUtilImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart">Resource Utilization</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_06_Resource_Utilization.svg" class="gstImg6" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">Resource Utilization helps you visualize the work allocated to users.</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeFinanceImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart">Finance</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_07_Finance.svg" class="gstImg7" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">You can create invoices of the approved timesheet, record your project budget and do much more with the Finance tab in Zoho Projects.</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeCalendarImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart">Calendar</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_08_Calendar.svg" class="gstImg8" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">Make the most of the calendar by marking important events, milestones, tasks, and issues. Sync tasks and events with iCalendar and Google Calendar</div> </div> </div> <div class="mauto img_div" id="welcomeReportsImg" onviewport="false"> <div class="mainholder"> <div class="tac text-white fs30px textpart">Reports</div> <div class="imgContainer"><img src="https://www.zoho.com/sites/default/files/projects/a_09_Reports.svg" class="gstImg9" style="transform: translate(390px, 60px) scale(0);"></div><div class="fs15px text-white tac lh22 textpart">With Reports, track your work progress, plan your work efficiently, and stay on top of your project.</div> </div> </div> <div class="posabsonly mauto flex L0 R0 w245" style="bottom:20%;"> <div class="w22 h22 pointer mr10 tac lh25imp fs11px zps-radius radius-50per prev_arrow disabled_arrow no-drop flex aic jcc" onclick="welcomePage.moveToLeft();"> <span class="zoho-down-arrow-plain pt3 pr1"></span> </div> <div class="slider_dots flex"> <div class="slider_dots-elem active_dot" onclick="welcomePage.moveToIndex(0)" data-tooltip="Tasks"></div> <div class="slider_dots-elem" onclick="welcomePage.moveToIndex(1)" data-tooltip="Timesheet"></div> <div class="slider_dots-elem" onclick="welcomePage.moveToIndex(2)" data-tooltip="Dependency"></div> <div class="slider_dots-elem" onclick="w